--[[
    AI Proxy Server Code
    
    This is Node.js code for a proxy server that connects to OpenAI API.
    You need to deploy this on a hosting service (Render, Railway, Glitch, etc.)
    
    INSTRUCTIONS:
    1. Create a new Node.js project
    2. Install dependencies: npm install express cors node-fetch dotenv
    3. Create .env file with your OpenAI API key
    4. Deploy to your hosting service
    5. Update PROXY_URL in AIAssistant script
]]

